snippet.title: Update 10.0 | Highlights
snippet.description:
www.warframe.com/signup
Ninjas Play Free.
Update 10 is coming! 
New Warframes - New Tileset - New combat - PLUS so much more 
In the final hours of Update 10, we visit  Steve Sinclair, Creative Director, and Scott McGregor, our Design Director. See what they have to say about soul punching, organ weapons and our deadly new Warframe, Nekros!
